t=\"Dependency Status\" data-canonical-src=\"https://david-dm.org/gaggle/validate.js-array.svg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p><code>array</code> validation plugin for <a href=\"http://validatejs.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">validate.js</a>.</p>\n<p>Install:</p>\n<pre><code>npm install gaggle/validate.js-array\n</code></pre>\n<p>Use:</p>\n<pre><code>var validate = require(\"validate.js\")\nrequire(\"validate.js-array\").register()\n\nvar schema = {\"foo\": {array: {bar: {presence: true}}}}\nvalidate({foo: [{bar: \"baz\"}]}, this.schema)\n// =&gt; undefined\n\nvalidate({foo: [{invalid: \"data\"}]}, this.schema)\n// =&gt; { foo: [ 'Foo element [{\"invalid\":\"data\"}] does not validate:\n        [{\"bar\":[\"Bar can\\'t be blank\"]}]' ] }\n</code></pre>\n</article></div>"